{
  "about": "KPR Institute of Engineering and Technology (KPRIET) is a premier autonomous engineering college established in 2009 by KPR Group of Industries, Coimbatore. It is approved by AICTE and affiliated to Anna University, Chennai. KPRIET offers eight UG programmes in Artificial Intelligence & Data Science, Biomedical, Chemical, Civil, Computer Science & Engineering, Electronics & Communication Engineering, Electrical & Electronics, and Mechanical Engineering and four PG Programmes. The institution is accredited by NAAC with 'A' Grade and Five UG Programmes are accredited by NBA. KPRIET is ranked among the top 200 Institutions in India and has a vision to provide world class engineering education and create Engineers, Technologists and Researchers to serve the nation and the globe.",
